The elegance lies in right assumptions/ substitution and elimination. The key invariant is the highest angle of the polygon. This value has to be lesser than 180 degrees (no internal angle of a polygon can be more than 180 degrees). The key move is to check the feasibility of the AP against the 180° ceiling — that constraint prunes the search space in one shot.”
